{"product_id":"berrichi-mist-face-spray-100ml","title":"BERRICHI Mist face spray 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis face spray is a luxurious daily skincare product that provides hydration to the skin, gives an instant feeling of freshness, and helps protect the skin from external stressors. The lightweight absorbent formula is suitable for daily use – for refreshing the skin in the morning, as well as for rehydrating throughout the day or for spraying over makeup. A delicately floral yet juicy fruity aroma – subtle elegance in every pump.\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProvides instant hydration and freshness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHelps even out skin tone and reduces melanin production\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmooths and tightens the skin, giving a more radiant appearance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStrengthens the skin’s natural protective barrier\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHelps restore the skin’s natural pH balance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran\u003c\/span\u003e – A powerful antioxidant that helps maintain skin moisture balance, strengthens the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the visible effects of aging, and reduces inflammation and dryness. Sourced from Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMineral-rich Seawater\u003c\/span\u003e – Packed with natural minerals and microelements, it revitalizes the skin and supports its natural balance. It strengthens the skin’s defense against pollution and environmental stressors, while offering anti-inflammatory benefits.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eChicory Root Extract\u003c\/span\u003e – A natural skin-tightening ingredient that provides an immediate smoothing effect. It stimulates collagen production and supports skin cell regeneration.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eSpreading Spiderwort\u003c\/span\u003e – Helps even out skin tone, reduces melanin production, and maintains the skin’s natural glow. It helps protect the skin from environmental damage\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eGolden Samphire\u003c\/span\u003e – A deeply hydrating agent that soothes and protects sensitive skin while reinforcing the skin’s natural barrier.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e – A soothing and hydrating ingredient with natural antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eShake before use. Hold the bottle 20–30 cm from your face and spray 2–3 times. Use in the morning, during the day, or as a makeup setting spray.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cichorium Intybus Root Oligosaccharides, Passiflora Edulis Fruit Water, Sea Salt, Orchis Morio Flower Water, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Propanediol, Sodium Benzoate, Polyglyceryl-6 Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate, Furcellaria Lumbricalis Extract, Citric Acid, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum, Gluconolactone, Sodium Levulinate, Boerhavia Diffusa Root Extract, Helichrysum Stoechas Callus Culture Lysate, Potassium Sorbate, Calcium Gluconate\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52137963094343,"sku":null,"price":21.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-mist-face-spray-100ml-3547408.png?v=1756222801","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/berrichi-mist-face-spray-100ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}